{
  "chapter": 153,
  "chapter_summary": "本章以滴血验亲开场，鹿公、徐先等军方重臣见证小盘与吕不韦的血滴不相融，证实小盘非吕不韦所出，军方对小盘的支持由此确立。随后项少龙私帐中，滕翼汇报已发现高陵君叛军藏于泾水上游\"七穴连珠\"山洞，项少龙利用吕不韦以为自己将死的心态，计划趁机行事。琴清听闻吕不韦将女儿嫁给项少龙的传言，醋意大发前来质问，项少龙在她耳边低声透露吕不韦下毒的阴谋，二人感情升温，琴清还讨要了一根飞针作纪念。渡河田猎时，项少龙与管中邪相遇，管中邪态度冷淡，暗示已决定除去鹿公，对鹿丹儿和嬴盈再无兴趣。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ying_ao",
      "text": "吕不韦这滴血怎得来的呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_ao",
      "speaker_name": "云阳君嬴傲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我拉他出去射箭，鹿公和王将军则在旁诈作斗耍，取了血他还不知是什么一回事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_gong",
      "speaker_name": "鹿公",
      "listener": "char_xu_xian",
      "text": "徐先！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "秦人的所谓田猎，对我这打了十多年猎的人来说只是一场闹剧，百里内的虎、狼都要被吓走。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "二哥为何不早点告诉我老虎早给吓得避难，那我就准备大批虎耳，以十倍价钱出售，让这批业余的猎者不致空手而回，保证供不应求，大大赚他娘的一笔。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "业余猎者！这形容确是古怪。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "高陵君的人躲在哪个洞里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "竟给三弟误打误撞碰对。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "此山林木深茂，位于泾水上游，有七个山洞，乡人称之为‘七穴连珠’，高陵君想得周到，就算明知他们藏在那里，也休想可找得着他们。我们只知他们在那里，但却没法把握到他们有多少人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "二哥真是夸大，把整个山区封锁，然后放火烧林，不是可把他们逼出来吗？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "text": "春雾湿重，这时候想烧林该是难比登天，噢！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "text": "除非烧的是乌大小姐的无名火，那又另当别论。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们的夫君死而复生，整个人变得佻皮起来。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不过他们若离开‘七穴连珠’，绝逃不过我们荆家猎手的耳目。嘿！我看该出动我们的儿郎，让他们多点机会争取实战的经验。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "这等事由二哥拿主意好了，幸好杜璧不在咸阳，否则形势将更复杂。嘻！横竖在吕不韦眼中，我只是个尚有两天半命的人，无论我在两天半内做什么，他都会忍一时之气，还要假情假意，好教人不怀疑是他害我，更重要是瞒着朱姬，在这种情况下，我若不去没事找事，就对不住真正的死鬼莫傲所想出来的这条毒计了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项郎你一天腿伤未愈，我们姊妹不容许你去逞强动手。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "text": "谁说过我要去和人动手争胜？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "text": "致妹他在耍弄你啊！快向他进攻，看他会否逞强动手。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_yan_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "乌言着",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "琴太傅到！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "清姊又不早点来，我们刚来了一场大决战哩！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "清姊有什么心事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我想和你们的夫君说两句话。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "过河的时间快到了，我们在外面备马等候你们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "什么事令太傅这么不高兴哩？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "琴清哪敢不高兴，还应恭喜项大人，娶得吕不韦如花似玉的宝贝女儿！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "琴太傅误会，这事内情错综复杂，吕不韦既不想把女儿嫁我，我也不会要这种女人为妻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那为何太后告诉我，吕不韦请她颁布你们的婚事，又说是你同意的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "琴太傅能否信任我一趟呢？田猎后你可由嫣然处得知事情始末。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "为何项大人说话总是吞吞吐吐、欲言又止、藏头露尾，你当琴清是什么人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "琴太傅想我项少龙当你是什么人呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人又想对琴清无礼吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "项少龙怎有这么大的胆子。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你究竟说还是不说？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "此乃天大秘密，不可传之二耳，所以琴太傅勿要怪我这样的和你说话儿。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人知道自己在干什么吗？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "那我说还是不说呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "因为吕不韦使人对我下毒，估量我绝活不过这两天，所以才诈作将女儿许配与我，还要昭告天下，那我若有不测，将没有人怀疑他，至少可瞒过太后。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "教琴太傅受惊了，幸好我识破他的阴谋，破去他下毒的手法，但此事吕不韦却懵然不知，仍将女儿嫁我，事后定然千方百计悔婚，那时太后就知他在骗她，所以我才佯作应允。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "差点吓死人家。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "多谢琴太傅关心。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "算我今趟错怪你吧！便与你刚才想借故对我无礼两下扯平，以后不许再犯。唔！弄得人家耳朵怪痒的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "琴太傅既明言不准我对你无礼，我会考虑一下，迟些告诉你我的决定好吗？不过这又是天大秘密，不可传于二耳。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你这人哪！真教人拿你没法。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "只要琴太傅不再整天为我动气便谢天谢地了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "要怪就怪你自己吧！什么事都不和琴清说清楚，不逼你就不肯说出来。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是了！刚才你一掷五针的事，传遍军营，人人皆知，我由太后帐内出来时，见到管中邪和嬴盈等在研究靶上的飞针。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人可否送一根飞针给琴清呢？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "再恕我无礼一次好吗？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "这是不想我项少龙把琴太傅当做外人的代价，以后我有空会来找我的红颜知己说心事话儿，什么有礼无礼都不理了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你有手有脚，欢喜来找琴清，又或不来找琴清，谁管得了你！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "text": "还以为管大人加入女儿军团哩！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "公务要紧，再不把她们赶跑，恐怕项大人降罪于我。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 153,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人一掷五针，力道平均，教人敬佩。",
